Dialogue: 10,0:00:02.48,0:00:03.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:03.41,0:00:05.02,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I was careless.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.02,0:00:08.35,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I deployed some personnel\N in the area around this house.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.35,0:00:11.53,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But they struck when \Nshe happened to be over here.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.45,0:00:14.90,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's the only thing left at the scene.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.90,0:00:18.51,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,They took her while she was using the bathroom.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.02,0:00:19.83,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,This is because...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.61,0:00:22.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,This is because I brought Sana{-chan} here!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.93,0:00:24.08,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.08,0:00:25.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.42,0:00:27.11,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It isn't your fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.58,0:00:30.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Ichijou{-kun} and a lady named\N Yamada are after them now.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.78,0:00:32.13,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they'll find her soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.13,0:00:34.35,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But... But...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.35,0:00:35.51,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.51,0:00:37.25,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Keep it together.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.25,0:00:38.05,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Grandpa...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.89,0:00:40.56,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She'll be fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.67,0:00:43.77,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.23,0:00:47.44,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana{-chan} is valuable to those guys, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.44,0:00:49.80,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,They won't be quick to harm her.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.23,0:00:51.68,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Harm her?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.08,0:00:53.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sanae...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.15,0:01:01.29,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.29,0:01:03.36,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Did you just imagine it now?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.41,0:01:09.67,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If you struggle or disobey me, you will die.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:11.22,0:01:13.48,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I would do absolutely anything
Dialogue: 10,0:01:13.94,0:01:16.06,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,to see him again.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.10,0:03:00.55,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What does everyone like about such a noisy place?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.15,0:03:05.24,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.24,0:03:07.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I want to go home and play video games.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.57,0:03:08.75,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We're done here, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.75,0:03:09.48,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.48,0:03:12.27,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We can leave the rest to Minnie C.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.27,0:03:14.63,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'll bring the Red Queen home.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.09,0:03:17.12,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You all did great.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.92,0:03:21.50,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If you get hungry before we get there,\N you can have that—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.50,0:03:22.68,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't want it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.81,0:03:25.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of sweet stuff.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.44,0:03:29.47,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,When this is over, \Neverything will be back to normal, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.47,0:03:31.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We'll be with Sana{-chan} again.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.94,0:03:32.48,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.65,0:03:34.90,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.54,0:03:45.74,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Honestly, you disappoint me.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.32,0:03:49.68,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You once commanded the principles of space itself.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.68,0:03:54.58,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If this is all you can do outside,\Nyou really are no more than a child.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.90,0:03:59.31,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You acquired a body, learned language, \Nand gained emotions...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.31,0:04:03.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Only to flee to the outside world \Nand pretend to be human.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.42,0:04:04.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.21,0:04:07.94,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It was so easy to render you motionless.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.27,0:04:11.08,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pretend to be human?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.08,0:04:13.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is she talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.02,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Or could it be...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.80,0:04:18.77,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you actually think you're human,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.46,0:04:22.53,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Red Queen?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.14,0:04:25.57,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Why are they after that girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.05,0:04:31.75,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I called you because I thought you could do something\Nabout the abuse she's apparently endured.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.75,0:04:36.63,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But it looks like you guys are \Nworking on something bigger.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.53,0:04:39.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's a state secret.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.21,0:04:39.88,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.88,0:04:41.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Kidding, kidding!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.03,0:04:42.05,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's just a joke.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.77,0:04:45.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,This is just something of a territorial dispute...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.64,0:04:50.51,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,In the government, \Ntwo people have two differing opinions.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.51,0:04:53.56,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm basically one of those people's lapdog.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.56,0:04:55.97,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Say it so I can understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.97,0:04:58.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Just what kind of little girl is she?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.43,0:05:02.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I'm not sure you'll believe me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.99,0:05:05.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But Sana{-chan}, most likely,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.85,0:05:08.66,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,isn't a human like you and me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.66,0:05:09.66,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.13,0:05:12.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You are not human.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.38,0:05:14.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,In fact...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.25,0:05:19.96,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Thirteen years ago, when you first \Nappeared beneath the research facility,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.96,0:05:23.17,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,you couldn't even be called a living thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.48,0:05:28.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You were a mere phenomenon that could \Nrandomly read thoughts and reactions
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.21,0:05:31.31,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,of living things around you, and make them real.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.71,0:05:33.02,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Your appearance,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.33,0:05:36.39,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,ego, emotions, and words you learned
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.39,0:05:38.90,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,were all cards that an ownerless Mirror Gate
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.90,0:05:42.47,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,created by copying those things from humans.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.47,0:05:43.98,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten that?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.98,0:05:45.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's a lie.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.07,0:05:47.72,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm Sana, and I'm right here!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.72,0:05:51.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That is why you must not leave the research facility.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.03,0:05:54.29,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Living in the outside world is impossible for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.29,0:05:57.01,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If there is a place for you in the world,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.01,0:05:59.25,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,it is at Wonderland and nowhere else.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.74,0:06:03.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Now, let us return to where you belong.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.16,0:06:08.49,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That girl's power is called a "Dream of Alice."
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.49,0:06:13.22,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And it's said that soon, \Nmany more people will have such powers.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.06,0:06:16.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,This may all sound preposterous.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.20,0:06:21.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But it flips our senses of vitality \Nand ethics totally upside-down.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.52,0:06:26.33,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Can our society accept beings like her?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.33,0:06:29.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We'll soon be facing that issue head-on.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.40,0:06:32.58,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Honestly, we think it's possible.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.58,0:06:35.38,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But the other side doesn't agree...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.85,0:06:37.83,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you understand now?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.73,0:06:40.11,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,More or less.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.11,0:06:43.79,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We'd been employing various tactics\N behind the scenes already.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.79,0:06:48.76,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And then we learned the girl we'd \Nbeen watching had wound up with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.28,0:06:52.72,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So I thought I'd make use of that little godsend.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.14,0:06:54.56,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Make use of it?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.26,0:07:00.09,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yep, to determine whether \Nhumans can coexist with Sana{-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.09,0:07:02.91,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess that's an exaggeration.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.91,0:07:07.56,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\q2}You've always been the kind of guy who \Ndoesn't consider the trouble he causes others.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.56,0:07:09.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.38,0:07:11.66,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll air my complaints later.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.66,0:07:14.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,After that girl comes back home.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.80,0:07:17.84,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sanae, can you continue to get along with her?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.84,0:07:18.58,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.58,0:07:19.71,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.71,0:07:21.00,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.39,0:07:23.05,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Then the girl can—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.05,0:07:26.05,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,U-Um, that's fine, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.05,0:07:31.18,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Grandpa, I wish you wouldn't just\N make decisions about everything
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.62,0:07:33.97,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,on your own like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.37,0:07:38.13,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,When I heard that Sana{-chan} was at our house,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.13,0:07:42.27,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I was really surprised.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.27,0:07:43.94,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's fine, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.94,0:07:47.57,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But you tend to be that way sometimes.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.60,0:07:49.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Do I?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.25,0:07:54.01,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Please value your family more!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.01,0:07:56.58,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Please talk to me more!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.20,0:08:01.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If we're going to be a family of three, \Nit's all the more reason.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.46,0:08:05.73,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm done.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.73,0:08:07.43,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.43,0:08:08.09,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.78,0:08:09.69,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.69,0:08:11.05,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm glad, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.08,0:08:16.22,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Now, then. Our little chat is over.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.62,0:08:19.81,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll need you to be quiet for a bit longer.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.78,0:08:23.12,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not human?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.12,0:08:26.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why I wasn't to go to the outside world?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.16,0:08:27.24,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.24,0:08:29.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I not allowed to go anywhere?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.46,0:08:32.46,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because I'm a monster?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.46,0:08:34.10,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.10,0:08:35.61,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.10,0:08:37.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}want that!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.03,0:08:39.65,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,This will just slow your body down,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.65,0:08:41.75,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,to make your brain stop working.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.12,0:08:46.25,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,When you're completely unconscious,\N you're more dangerous.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.62,0:08:50.72,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Filthy...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.52,0:09:01.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh, you've come here?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.14,0:09:05.39,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's sort of against the rules for you to talk to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.29,0:09:08.75,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I feel like I know you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.75,0:09:09.48,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.97,0:09:11.27,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.27,0:09:13.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Well... let's see.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.42,0:09:16.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm a really cool lady you don't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.64,0:09:17.58,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.58,0:09:20.74,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,When I was at the research facility, \Ndid you talk to me?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.43,0:09:24.33,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Well, in time, you'll find out.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.80,0:09:26.66,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So flat.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.66,0:09:27.79,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.79,0:09:31.51,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You're an adult, \Nbut Sanae has bigger breasts than you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.51,0:09:33.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You'd better not forget you said that.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.85,0:09:35.55,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll knock you for a loop later.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.74,0:09:38.61,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.39,0:09:42.57,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I may not be human.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.57,0:09:43.89,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I may be a monster.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.42,0:09:49.12,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Most people don't know what they really are.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.12,0:09:51.94,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm still searching for that myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.83,0:09:55.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't tell you this.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.78,0:09:59.17,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But I was very lucky.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.17,0:10:02.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I had people around me who knew things I didn't.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.51,0:10:05.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you do, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.96,0:10:08.95,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You should try calling that person's name.
Comment: 10,0:10:11.93,0:10:13.14,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{random vocalization}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.74,0:10:16.57,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you just hear something?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.57,0:10:17.17,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.17,0:10:19.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Look above you. Above.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.03,0:10:20.27,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.27,0:10:21.51,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The hell is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.01,0:10:23.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's Sana{-chan}'s.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.14,0:10:27.23,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.23,0:10:29.44,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Please save Sana{-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.44,0:10:30.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.02,0:10:33.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zou... roku.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.20,0:10:38.24,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.25,0:10:52.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.47,0:10:55.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.52,0:10:56.96,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana, you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.31,0:10:58.69,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.69,0:11:00.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.19,0:11:02.58,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the first time he's called me "Sana."
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.58,0:11:07.39,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you the one who's \Nbeen cruel to this little girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.94,0:11:10.18,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Honestly, Red Queen,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.18,0:11:11.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,all you do is cause—
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.21,0:11:13.24,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You demon...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.24,0:11:14.69,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm not joking here!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.40,0:11:19.95,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I hate crooked stuff!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.52,0:11:22.95,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Just who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.95,0:11:24.77,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm a florist.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.77,0:11:27.58,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But I'm not going to lose to some kid.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.33,0:11:29.04,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.04,0:11:31.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Where's your energy from earlier?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.66,0:11:34.57,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Can't you do anything, just by thinking about it?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.57,0:11:37.25,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So don't just stay here like this!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.02,0:11:41.02,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.18,0:11:44.35,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Get back home right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.35,0:11:48.98,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That creepy guy, Naitou, is gonna save you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.48,0:11:52.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.78,0:11:53.56,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Just...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.64,0:11:55.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Get going, now!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.52,0:11:57.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Would you please be quiet?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.85,0:11:58.23,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.92,0:12:05.99,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.50,0:12:07.79,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.28,0:12:14.46,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Red Queen,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.84,0:12:17.75,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,if you try to act on your own again,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.75,0:12:19.80,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,something even worse will happen.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.26,0:12:22.10,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Next time, to him.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.10,0:12:23.09,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.09,0:12:24.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.45,0:12:26.18,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I am entirely serious.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.18,0:12:27.55,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana. Sana...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.02,0:12:29.31,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.31,0:12:30.32,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.32,0:12:31.72,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No more!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.72,0:12:34.14,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did it come to this?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.14,0:12:37.08,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because I'm not human?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.08,0:12:39.97,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because I pretended to be human when I'm not,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.97,0:12:42.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I called Zouroku here?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.62,0:12:45.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or because Zouroku and I...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.05,0:12:48.25,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.00,0:12:50.04,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I get it.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.78,0:13:07.04,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.07,0:13:09.39,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.03,0:13:13.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So don't do anything bad to Zouroku.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.19,0:13:15.81,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.81,0:13:16.57,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.57,0:13:18.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Her energy finally ran out.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.19,0:13:19.06,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.06,0:13:21.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Is your wound okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.00,0:13:24.82,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She truly is amazing.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.53,0:13:28.53,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,While making her wound disappear,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.53,0:13:31.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,she actually rewrote parts of her situation.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.58,0:13:36.73,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I've located Sana{-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.73,0:13:39.96,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She's headed toward Oi Futo on the\N Shuto Expressway Bayshore Route!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.96,0:13:40.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.93,0:13:45.38,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll ask an acquaintance in Port Authority \Nif he's seen anyone strange leaving Oi.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.08,0:13:47.91,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Ichijou{-kun}, did you hear that?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.91,0:13:49.60,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes! I'll head there too!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.02,0:13:51.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.45,0:13:52.73,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So there you go.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.73,0:13:54.74,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Nothing to worry about anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.74,0:13:56.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.45,0:13:58.56,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm heading out for a bit.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.56,0:14:00.82,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You should go home for now, Sanae{-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.82,0:14:02.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll get someone to take you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.10,0:14:04.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Wait here.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.06,0:14:21.13,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.13,0:14:24.38,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Could you take me with you?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.46,0:14:36.43,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Zouroku.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.96,0:14:41.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I... really am... a monster.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.19,0:14:42.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.62,0:14:44.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Zouroku.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.30,0:14:46.89,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.89,0:14:48.15,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.16,0:14:50.36,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.93,0:14:56.15,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Kashimura Zouroku{-san}, age 72.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.15,0:14:59.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Owner of the flower shop Kashimura Floral.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.21,0:15:03.04,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Your family consists of a granddaughter, \Nwho is a high school junior.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.64,0:15:05.96,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You know all about me, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.60,0:15:11.74,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'd appreciate it if you would\N quietly accompany us for a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.74,0:15:13.76,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Who are you, anyway?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.27,0:15:17.14,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I am Miriam C. Tachibana.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.14,0:15:22.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I'm working with a certain state project that \Ninvolves the Japanese and American governments.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.10,0:15:25.65,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The "Dreams of Alice," right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.65,0:15:27.72,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh, you know of them?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.72,0:15:30.81,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Our goal is to research the Dreams of Alice
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.81,0:15:33.91,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,and artificially reproduce their powers.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.91,0:15:38.25,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And in the end, we'll build a new \Nenergy system based upon it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.86,0:15:41.67,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You could say this is a project to benefit humanity.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.67,0:15:46.31,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You don't mind keeping this child locked up \Nfor life, dissecting her or anything else,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.31,0:15:49.17,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,as long as it's "to benefit humanity"?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.50,0:15:52.74,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You like sci-fi movies, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.26,0:15:55.38,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We will not dissect her.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.38,0:15:56.43,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.21,0:16:01.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She is not a human, let alone a child.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.70,0:16:09.71,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The Red Queen is an unknown phenomenon,\Nborn when an unidentified being mimicked humans.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.71,0:16:10.46,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Bah!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.46,0:16:11.92,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a load of nonsense to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.92,0:16:14.11,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She looks like an ordinary little girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.11,0:16:19.60,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\q2}What if a WMD adopted an artificial personality,\N taking the form of a young girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.86,0:16:23.33,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What would you think about that?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.33,0:16:24.08,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.08,0:16:29.55,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Such a monster is attempting \Nto mingle in our society, in disguise.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.55,0:16:30.61,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.61,0:16:33.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Kashimura{-san}, since meeting her,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.16,0:16:36.65,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,have you or your granddaughter\N been in mortal danger?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.65,0:16:39.22,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't listen to a word she says!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.22,0:16:41.25,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey, everything you're saying is—
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.25,0:16:42.32,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.81,0:16:45.71,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Zouroku...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.43,0:16:50.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I think it's true that I'm a monster!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.52,0:16:52.76,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,There are lots of things I thought were strange.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.76,0:16:53.15,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.15,0:16:55.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm a monster.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.81,0:17:00.29,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If you find out what I really am,\N I'm sure you'll hate me, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.29,0:17:03.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,M-Maybe you already hate me now.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.89,0:17:11.17,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't want you or Sanae to go through\N any more trouble because of me.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.17,0:17:12.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sana...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.07,0:17:16.08,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If it was all because I wanted to be human,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.76,0:17:19.35,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,then you don't... need me around.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.42,0:17:22.18,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Zouroku.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.18,0:17:25.01,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll go back to the research facility.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.53,0:17:26.67,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.55,0:17:29.36,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The food was delicious!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.06,0:17:36.68,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.68,0:17:38.15,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm taking a helicopter there!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.15,0:17:39.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.03,0:17:40.47,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll go on my own.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.47,0:17:42.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That'll be faster.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.30,0:17:47.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, you're so badass!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.30,0:17:51.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I found out which boat they're on.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.16,0:17:53.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Ichijou{-kun} will save them in no time.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.62,0:17:54.88,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.88,0:17:56.92,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine, really.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.92,0:18:00.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Right now, I bet your grandpa's \Nlecturing the kidnapper.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.86,0:18:04.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,He's saying, "I hate crooked stuff!"
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.13,0:18:11.54,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Back then...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.25,0:18:14.48,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What're you making?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.48,0:18:17.56,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,They're graves.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.41,0:18:22.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\t(2995,3955,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}I don't clearly remember
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.41,0:18:25.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,what Grandpa said to me then.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.20,0:18:26.08,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.71,0:18:32.13,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Earlier, when he said that Sana{-chan} \Nmight become part of our family,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.59,0:18:39.04,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I had a really strange feeling,\Nlike something tightening in my chest.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.46,0:18:41.60,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.48,0:18:48.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I think that it made me remember a little bit.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.60,0:18:52.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What Grandpa told me back then,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.45,0:18:55.10,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,at the time of my parents' funeral.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.10,0:18:59.02,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And how much his words saved me.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.02,0:19:00.61,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Listen...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.61,0:19:01.61,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.61,0:19:05.33,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Even if you aren't human, so what?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.33,0:19:06.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't say such dumb things.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.32,0:19:13.67,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Just come home with me now, Sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.96,0:19:19.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You said your name's Miriam{-san}?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.42,0:19:22.58,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You said this girl isn't human.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.34,0:19:26.72,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Then, let me ask... What is a human?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.72,0:19:29.74,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You shot a child, without a thought. \NCan you be considered human?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.53,0:19:32.77,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That is not the issue here.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.27,0:19:36.05,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You're right that this girl's dangerous.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.05,0:19:39.17,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The moment I take my eyes off her, \Nshe's causing a commotion.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.17,0:19:41.12,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,At best, she's a nuisance.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.77,0:19:45.24,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But everyone does those things.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.86,0:19:49.54,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,As long as you see the problem\N and improve, it's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.54,0:19:50.96,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.96,0:19:52.37,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Not to mention,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.81,0:19:54.38,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,she's happy when she has good food.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.18,0:19:57.59,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,In her own clumsy way, she worries about others.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.59,0:19:59.05,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And she even gauges others' moods.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.46,0:20:01.47,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Even when she's caused trouble,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.47,0:20:04.55,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,she's never done anything with malicious intent.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.27,0:20:07.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's who Sana is.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.40,0:20:09.02,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She's got a heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.45,0:20:13.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,As I was saying, the issue here\N is not such a personal matter.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.87,0:20:16.77,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You aren't in any position to do anything with her—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.77,0:20:19.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Listen when your elders speak!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.91,0:20:23.96,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,All of us, no matter who, are imperfect somehow.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.96,0:20:27.01,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,There are things we can't know or do on our own,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.01,0:20:29.91,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,so we lean on each other to get by.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.92,0:20:32.83,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Isn't that true for you, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.83,0:20:38.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Look, even if this girl is some \Nkind of alien, like you say,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.85,0:20:41.80,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,is that really a problem?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.80,0:20:45.18,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You honestly don't think coexistence is possible?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.22,0:20:50.27,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Zouroku...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.58,0:20:52.01,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.01,0:20:54.83,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm not human, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.83,0:20:57.94,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll cause a lot of trouble for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.94,0:20:59.46,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,For Sanae, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.23,0:21:02.15,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.15,0:21:03.80,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,No matter what you are,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.80,0:21:06.49,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,in tough times, you should be with others.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.80,0:21:10.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't force yourself, Sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.02,0:21:17.33,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,In any case, I have no reason to send \Nyou away with these violent fools!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.12,0:21:21.63,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You left because you wanted \Nto see what was outside, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.22,0:21:23.99,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Then do that.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.99,0:21:25.47,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't go back on your word.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.98,0:21:29.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I hate crooked stuff, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.60,0:21:39.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Y-You must be an idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.86,0:21:40.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.56,0:21:51.12,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.80,0:21:54.44,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm here to save you.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.08,0:21:59.79,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm Cabinet Information Research Office \NSecret Service agent Ichijou Shizuku.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.82,0:22:04.02,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We'll be taking you two with us!
